OL,3,CBowling club appeals for more people
OL,4,Cto take up the sport
OL,6,FCumbrian bowlers say local club is
OL,7,Fvital to their mental and physical
OL,8,Fhealth as they appeal for more members
OL,9,Fto sign up.
OL,11,FThe Cumbria Indoor Bowls Club, in
OL,12,FCarlisle, are appealing for more
OL,13,Fpeople to improve their health and
OL,14,Fstart playing. The organisation's
OL,15,Fmembership numbers have more than
OL,16,Fhalved from a few thousands a few
OL,17,Fyears ago, now to around 600 members.
OL,19,FAlan Causar, 85, says the friendship
OL,20,Ffound at the club has helped him cope
OL,21,Fwith the loss of his wife.
