OL,3,CBowling club appeals for more people
OL,4,Cto take up the sport
OL,6,FHe said: "It's a godsend to me, it
OL,7,Freally is. I used to play a lot of
OL,8,Fgolf but I can't do that now. I lost
OL,9,Fmy wife seven years ago in June, that
OL,10,Fwas a big loss.
OL,12,FMartin Kennedy, bowler and volunteer
OL,13,Fat Age UK, believes older people have
OL,14,Fbeen hesitant to get involved due to
OL,15,Fthe stay at home habits which became
OL,16,Fprevalent during the pandemic.
