OL,3,CBowling club appeals for more people
OL,4,Cto take up the sport
OL,6,FHe said: "We've found that based on
OL,7,Four experience as an organisation that
OL,8,Fsince Covid there's been a reluctance
OL,9,Ffrom older people to leave their
OL,10,Fhomes, resulting in a loss of
OL,11,Fconfidence and self-esteem.
OL,13,F"So by giving momentum to hopefully
OL,14,Frecruiting some new members, it may
OL,15,Fencourage people to come out and meet
OL,16,Fnew friends in a social environment."
OL,18,FThe not-for-profit organisation will
OL,19,Fbe celebrating their 50 year
OL,20,Fanniversary next year.
